description: Maximize total productive capacity at the end of the five years. The problem parameters are a matrix of coefficients InputOne, a vector of manpower coefficients for input one ManpowerOne, a matrix of coefficients InputTwo, a vector of manpower coefficients for input two Manpowertwo, initial stock levels Stock, productive capacities Capacity, a company-wide manpower limit ManpowerLimit, and demand for each productive unit Demand.
